title: BRMW - Online Database Modeling
Og_description: Online and open source tool for database modeling
Banner_help_content: You can help keep BRMW alive.
Hero_tagline: Create conceptual or logical database models and export SQL code right from your browser
Features_easy_to_use_content: The friendly and intuitive interface allows you to use the tool without complications
Features_access_from_anywhere_content: Your projects stored in the cloud and available from any device, anywhere
Features_convert_in_seconds_content: Build and convert between conceptual, logical and physical (SQL) levels
Features_visualize_relationships_content: Use the relationship entity diagram to represent connections and entities

Support_title: How can you support the project?
Support_github_star_content: More stars on Github means greater visibility for the project and this helps us increase our reach.
Support_suggestions_content: Suggesting improvements helps us better understand user needs.
Support_report_bugs_content: All software has bugs. Reporting issues helps us improve the experience for all users.
Support_coding_content: If you have experience with programming or want to learn, you are welcome to contribute to the project code.
Support_donate_content: This helps us cover the project's operating costs, including server, database, email sending services, among other things.
Github_stargazers_content: brmodeloweb/brmodelo-app has more than 700 stars on GitHub
